       "data": "2 \\pi  \\text{$\\sigma $p} \\text{$\\sigma $x} \\exp \\left(-\\frac{1}{2} \\text{kx}^2 \\text{$\\sigma $x}^2-\\frac{(\\text{kp} m+\\text{kx} (\\text{t1}+\\text{t2})) \\left(\\text{$\\sigma $p}^2 (\\text{kp} m+\\text{kx} (\\text{t1}+\\text{t2}))+2 i m q\\right)}{2 m^2}\\right)",
