       "data": "\\sqrt{2 \\pi } \\text{$\\sigma $p} \\cos \\left(\\frac{q u}{\\hbar }\\right) \\cos \\left(\\frac{q (2 m u+q \\text{t1})}{2 m \\hbar }\\right) e^{-\\frac{q^2 \\text{$\\sigma $p}^2 \\text{t1}^2}{2 m^2 \\hbar ^2}-\\frac{u^2}{2 \\text{$\\sigma $x}^2}}",
